ther! Simply pair TJ\'s Pomegranate Lime Juice with your favorite brand of Tequila, and you\'ll be enjoying summer in no time!','Hard Pomegranate','Warm-weather favorite with TJ\'s Pomegranate Lime Juice and Tequila','publish','open','open','','hard-pomegranate','','','2015-04-28 21:30:14','2015-04-28 21:30:14','',0,'http://staging.tjscocktails.com/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=767',0,'recipe','',0),(768,1,'2015-04-28 21:18:36','2015-04-28 21:18:36','When I lived in Southern California, one of my favorite places to enjoy Happy Hour was the Rockin\' Baja Lobster on Newport Beach. An afternoon spent there was never complete without a pitcher of Baja Bombers! This delicious blend ofTrader Jos Premium Lager,Trader Jos\'s Classic Margarita, and your favorite Tequila is sure to become one of your summertime favorites!\r\n\r\n(Party Tip- For a good time, you can triple the recipe in a pitcher and drink it through long straws like a fish-bowl!)','Baja Bomber','Warm-weather cocktail with Trader Jos Premium Lager, Trader Jos\'s Classic Margarita, and Tequila','publish','open','open','','baja-bomber','','','2015-04-28 21:29:28','2015-04-28 21:29:28','',0,'http://staging.tjscocktails.com/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=768',0,'recipe','',0),(769,1,'2015-04-28 21:17:41','2015-04-28 21:17:41','Trader Joe\'s seasonal favorite, Watermelon Cucumber Juice is a refreshing treat as the weather gets warmer. Add a little of your favorite Gin, and get your summer started!','Watermelon Cooler','Warm-weather cocktail with TJ\'s Watermelon Cucumber Juice and Gin','publish','open','open','','watermelon-cooler','','','2015-04-28 21:31:36','2015-04-28 21:31:36','',0,'http://staging.tjscocktails.com/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=769',0,'recipe','',0),(770,1,'2015-04-28 21:36:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Welcome!','','draft','open','open','','','','','2015-04-28 21:36:13','2015-04-28 21:36:13','',0,'http://staging.tjscocktails.com/?p=770',0,'post','',0),(771,1,'2015-04-28 21:36:13','2015-04-28 21:36:13','','Welc